metadata.name: Where is Pepe ?
metadata.description:
#WHEREISPEPE 1st

In NFT world we introduce its collectors to Pepe, who is dressed differently as he takes a "walk around the world". Pepe travels to everyday places like the beach, the ski slopes and the zoo. And wherever he goes, he somehow manages to lose more of his belongings or himself in order to be found. 

In these works, we show you Pepe's meeting with the Doodle world in different works. Let's find Pepe in the Doodle world...

5000x5000 px
300 Dpi
Handmade Drawing

''We will send our signed artwork to the first bidder!!!''
